==Headslapper==

===Etymology===
'''Headslapper''' is a slang term which appears to have originated in the Bitmines group on [[w:Internet CB Network|ICB]], the [[w:Internet CB Network|Internet CB Network]].&nbsp; The term may have been originated by the Reverend J. B. Bell.&nbsp; In the admittedly sometimes-odd context of Bitmines, it's about equal parts derogatory and compliment.

It is canonically explained approximately as follows:

'You're out somewhere, and you see this ravishingly, stunningly gorgeous [person of the desired sex], and you think to yourself, "Gad, I'd give my left [insert body part here] to date him/her."&nbsp; Then thirty seconds later, you slap yourself upside the head and say, "What was I thinking?!?" when you remember that he/she is barking mad.'

===Noun===
''(headslapper)''  (''plural:'' ''(headslappers)'')
# A person you consider extremely physically desirable, but far too unstable to risk involvement with


